                          <p style="height:30px;color:white;background-color:#0066CC;border:1px;">This page has been archived and commenting is disabled.</p>                        <h1 class="title">Krieger On Peak Government</h1>
            <div class="tabs"></div>
            <div class="node">
  <div class="picture">
  <a href="/users/tyler-durden" title="View user profile."><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/pictures/picture-5.jpg" alt="Tyler Durden&#039;s picture" title="Tyler Durden&#039;s picture"  /></a></div>

  
  <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/users/tyler-durden">Tyler Durden</a> on  06/16/2011 14:33 -0400</span><br /><br /><span class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_194 first"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/194" rel="tag" title="">Bill Gross</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_10414"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/10414" rel="tag" title="">Bond</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_139"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/139" rel="tag" title="China">China</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_11131"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/11131" rel="tag" title="">CRAP</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_9344"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/9344" rel="tag" title="">Fail</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_9586"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/9586" rel="tag" title="">Great Depression</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_9219"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/9219" rel="tag" title="">Gross Domestic Product</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_8436"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/8436" rel="tag" title="">Japan</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_10014"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/10014" rel="tag" title="">Monetary Policy</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_11670"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/11670" rel="tag" title="">Nominal GDP</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_8749"><a href="/taxonomy_vtn/term/8749" rel="tag" title="">Purchasing Power</a></li>
