  <a href="/users/freedomguy" title="View user profile."><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/pictures/picture-30064.jpg" alt="FreedomGuy&#039;s picture" title="FreedomGuy&#039;s picture"  /></a></div>
