<p>Mass-produce a long range radio (phased array?) that can create an internet connection with any other such radios within range.&nbsp; Data should be encoded over&nbsp;a wide band&nbsp;which should be easily hackable to a huge band, even outside the ham radio bands.&nbsp; This would make jamming more difficult.&nbsp; Maybe you could even disguise the data as lightning strikes.&nbsp; Trouble is, I rather doubt this system would be cheap, and I doubt your authorities would approve.</p>
